## Get Airtable Data in Obsidian with AI Agent
<-- Watch the video to see it in action!

**How to Set Up:**
- Install the [Post Webhook Plugin]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }} in Obsidian.
- Insert the n8n Webhook URL into the Post Webhook plugin settings.
- Configure Your Airtable Node to match your workflow needs.


**How to Use:**
- Highlight text containing a question about your Airtable data.
- Open the Obsidian Command Palette (Ctrl+P) and choose 'Send Selection to [Your Webhook]'.
- Click, wait for the AI Agent to process your request, and see the result appear below your selected text.

# Get Airtable data in Obsidian Notes

## Overview
Automated workflow: Get Airtable data in Obsidian Notes. This workflow integrates 7 different services: webhook, stickyNote, agent, respondToWebhook, stopAndError. It contains 12 nodes and follows best practices for error handling and security.

## Workflow Details
- **Total Nodes**: 12
- **Node Types**: 7
- **Error Handling**: ✅ Implemented
- **Security**: ✅ Hardened (no sensitive data)
- **Documentation**: ✅ Complete

## Node Breakdown
- **Airtable**: airtableTool
- **OpenAI Chat Model**: lmChatOpenAi
- **AI Agent**: agent
- **Sticky Note**: stickyNote
- **Sticky Note1**: stickyNote
- **Respond to Obsidian**: respondToWebhook
- **Webhook Set Up in Obsidian**: webhook
- **Error Handler**: stopAndError
- **Stopanderror 1**: stopAndError
- **Error Handler for 8a100c92**: stopAndError
- ... and 2 more nodes

## Usage Instructions
1. **Configure Credentials**: Set up all required API keys and credentials
2. **Update Variables**: Replace any placeholder values with actual data
3. **Test Workflow**: Run in test mode to verify functionality
4. **Deploy**: Activate the workflow for production use

## Security Notes
- All sensitive data has been removed or replaced with placeholders
- Error handling is implemented for reliability
- Follow security best practices when configuring credentials

## Troubleshooting
- Check error logs if workflow fails
- Verify all credentials are properly configured
- Ensure all required services are accessible
